FBIS4-10375 "drlat070_o_94006" FBIS-LAT-94-070 Daily Report 10 Apr 1994 Colombia Armed Forces Disagree With General's Sentence Armed Forces Disagree With General's Sentence PA1104164494 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 in Spanish 0130 GMT 10 Apr 94 PA1104164494 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 Spanish BFN [From the "TV Today" newscast] [Text] Major General Hernan Jose Guzman, Army commander, said that Armed Forces members will obey the sentence given by the Attorney General's Office to General Jesus Armando Arias Cabrales for his conduct in the Justice Palace takeover, but they do not agree with it. [Begin Guzman recording] We do not think it is right that those of us who defend the nation on the front line are also the ones who are punished. [end recording]
